# Login & Signup Form with Bootstrap

## Overview
This project is a simple Login and Signup Form built using HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and JavaScript.
 The form includes a modern UI with icons, password visibility toggle, and smooth transitions between login and signup sections.

## Features
- Responsive Design: Fully responsive using Bootstrap.
- Login & Signup Forms: Two separate forms for authentication.
- Password Toggle: Users can show/hide passwords.
- Remember Me Option: Checkbox for remembering user credentials.
- Form Transitions: JavaScript-based toggle between Login and Signup forms.
- FontAwesome Icons: Used for email, password, and visibility toggle.

## Technologies Used
- HTML: Structure of the form
- CSS: Styling for better UI
- Bootstrap 5: For responsive layout and components
- FontAwesome: Icons for inputs
- JavaScript: Toggle functionality for form switching


